ENDJOB

AIX_JOB LIE.!ESPAPPL
   AGENT CYBA_ISBFP3
   COMMAND /bin/sleep
   ARGS 3
   USER bfpadm
   RUN DAILY
   NOTIFY JOBEND MAILBOX(AKRONJOBREQ) +
   SUBJECT('BWDAUDIT - APPLICATION BWDAUDIT HAS COMPLETED')
